ontrols.Button.OnClick%2A> event handler for the button defined in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](../../../../includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] for this example.  \n  \n [!code-csharp[TextBox_MiscCode#_SelectText](../../../../samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_Wpf/TextBox_MiscCode/CSharp/Window1.xaml.cs#_selecttext)]\n [!code-vb[TextBox_MiscCode#_SelectText](../../../../samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_Wpf/TextBox_MiscCode/VisualBasic/Window1.xaml.vb#_selecttext)]  \n  \n## See Also  \n [TextBox Overview](../../../../docs/framework/wpf/controls/textbox-overview.md)   \n [RichTextBox Overview](../../../../docs/framework/wpf/controls/richtextbox-overview.md)","nodes":[{"pos":[4,469],"nodes":[{"content":"How to: Retrieve a Text Selection | Microsoft Docs","nodes":[{"pos":[0,50],"content":"How to: Retrieve a Text Selection | Microsoft Docs","nodes":[{"content":"How to: Retrieve a Text Selection | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,50]}]}],"pos":[6,59],"yaml":true}],"content":"title: \"How to: Retrieve a Text Selection | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nms.prod: \".net-framework\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"dotnet-wpf\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"text, retrieving\"\n  - \"TextBox control, retrieving text\"\n  - \"retrieving text\"\nms.assetid: d5793172-1e11-4a39-9be0-73f336ed858d\ncaps.latest.revision: 10\nauthor: dotnet-bot\nms.author: dotnetcontent\nmanager: \"wpickett\"","yamlblock":true},{"pos":[476,509],"content":"How to: Retrieve a Text Selection","linkify":"How to: Retrieve a Text Selection","nodes":[{"content":"How to: Retrieve a Text Selection","pos":[0,33]}]},{"content":"This example shows one way to use the <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox.SelectedText%2A&gt;</ph> property to retrieve text that the user has selected in a <ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox&gt;</ph> control.","pos":[510,708],"source":"This example sh